==Korean==

===Noun===
'''두꺼비''' (dukkeobi) 
# [[toad]] 

====Related terms====
* [[두껍다]] (''duKkeobda, duKkeopda'') To be [[thick]]
* [[두께]] (''duKke'') [[thickness]] cf. German [[Dicke]]
* [[두터비]] (''duteobi'') (obsolete) [[toad]] cf. Old English [[tāda]], [[tādiġe]] (of unknown origin)
* [[두텁다]] (''duteobda, duteopda'') To be [[thick]]
* [[두툴두툴]] (''dutul-dutul'') Being [[rugged]], [[rough]] (of bark, skin, etc.) 
* [[두툼]]하다 (''dutum-hada'') To [[bulge]] slightly
* [[둑]] (''dug, duk'') [[dike]] cf. [[thick]], German [[dick]]
* [[둔]] ([[屯]], ''dun'') [[dune]] cf. [[thin]], German [[dünn]]  

